    "3) To the best of our knowledge, we are the first to perform an indepth analysis of unlearnable text datasets, where our model agnostic approach is highly effective at limiting the learning of state-of-the-art LLMs like GPT-4o and Llama-3.1 on fine-tuning tasks.",
